      <title>欧洲央行行长武伊西奇表示开始降息前需要耐心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/ecb-s-vujcic-says-patience-needed-before-starting-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员鲍里斯·武伊西奇表示，欧洲央行官员需要确保在降息之前工资不会对通胀产生任何第二轮影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/ecb-s-vujcic-says-patience-needed-before-starting-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 14:58:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
